<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Hakkimizda - OnSuite | <%= data.site.title %></title>
  <meta name="description" content="Siskon Otomasyon - 20+ yillik endustriyel otomasyon deneyimi ile akilli uretim cozumleri.">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/design-system.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/pages.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/inner.css">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/assets/images/favicon.png">
</head>
<body>

<%- include('partials/header') %>

<!-- ABOUT HERO -->
<section class="inner-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="inner-hero__title">Fabrikalar Icin Yazilim Yapiyoruz</h1>
    <p class="inner-hero__desc">Siskon Otomasyon olarak 20+ yildir endustriyel otomasyon alaninda calisiyoruz. OnSuite, bu deneyimin yazilim urunune donusmesi.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TIMELINE / STORY -->
<section class="about-story">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-story__grid">
      <div class="about-story__item">
        <span class="about-story__year">2003</span>
        <h3 class="about-story__heading">Siskon Otomasyon Kurulusu</h3>
        <p class="about-story__text">Izmir'de endustriyel otomasyon alaninda faaliyete basladik. PLC programlama, SCADA sistemleri ve saha otomasyonu ile uretim tesislerini dijitallestirmeye basladik.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-story__item">
        <span class="about-story__year">2010</span>
        <h3 class="about-story__heading">MES Vizyonu</h3>
        <p class="about-story__text">Sahada edindigimiz tecrube ile uretim yonetim sistemi (MES) gelistirmeye basladik. Fabrika verisini anlam ifade eden bilgiye donusturme hedefiyle yola ciktik.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-story__item">
        <span class="about-story__year">2018</span>
        <h3 class="about-story__heading">OnSuite Platformu</h3>
        <p class="about-story__text">Moduler, olceklenebilir ve bulut destekli OnSuite platformunu piyasaya sunduk. 8 modul ile uretimin her asamasini tek ekrandan yonetilebilir hale getirdik.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-story__item">
        <span class="about-story__year">2024</span>
        <h3 class="about-story__heading">Global Buyume</h3>
        <p class="about-story__text">40+ ulkede, 100+ projede, 500+ uretim hattinda aktif kullanim. Bosch, BSH, Unilever, Philip Morris gibi global markalarla calisiyoruz.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- KEY NUMBERS -->
<section class="inner-stats" style="background:#FAFBFC">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="inner-stats__grid">
      <div class="inner-stats__item">
        <span class="inner-stats__value" style="color:#0089CF">40+</span>
        <span class="inner-stats__label">Ulke</span>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-stats__item">
        <span class="inner-stats__value" style="color:#04bf8a">100+</span>
        <span class="inner-stats__label">Proje</span>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-stats__item">
        <span class="inner-stats__value" style="color:#ff3b78">500+</span>
        <span class="inner-stats__label">Uretim Hatti</span>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-stats__item">
        <span class="inner-stats__value" style="color:#034082">20+</span>
        <span class="inner-stats__label">Yillik Deneyim</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- VALUES -->
<section class="about-values">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="inner-section-title">Degerlerimiz</h2>
    <div class="about-values__grid">
      <div class="about-values__card">
        <div class="about-values__icon" style="color:#0089CF">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="about-values__name">Saha Deneyimi</h3>
        <p class="about-values__desc">Yazilimi ofiste degil, fabrika sahasinda gelistiriyoruz. Gercek problemleri gercek cozumlerle karsiliyor.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-values__card">
        <div class="about-values__icon" style="color:#04bf8a">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="about-values__name">Sonuc Odakli</h3>
        <p class="about-values__desc">Teknoloji satmiyoruz, sonuc satiyoruz. OEE artisi, fire azalma, izlenebilirlik — olculebilir degerler.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-values__card">
        <div class="about-values__icon" style="color:#ff3b78">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2M9 11a4 4 0 100-8 4 4 0 000 8zM23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="about-values__name">Uzun Vadeli Ortaklik</h3>
        <p class="about-values__desc">Musterilerimizle proje degil, ortaklik kuruyoruz. Devreye alimdan sonra da yaniinizdayiz.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CONTACT INFO -->
<section class="about-contact">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-contact__grid">
      <div class="about-contact__info">
        <h2 class="inner-section-title" style="text-align:left">Iletisim</h2>
        <div class="about-contact__item">
          <strong>Adres</strong>
          <p>Siskon Otomasyon, Izmir, Turkiye</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-contact__item">
          <strong>Telefon</strong>
          <p><a href="tel:+902322450076">+90 (232) 245 00 76</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-contact__item">
          <strong>E-posta</strong>
          <p><a href="mailto:info@siskon.com.tr">info@siskon.com.tr</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-contact__cta">
        <h3>Projelerinizi Konusalim</h3>
        <p>Uretim hattinizi dijitallestirmek icin ilk adimi atin.</p>
        <a href="/demo" class="btn btn--primary">Demo Talep Et <span>&rarr;</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
<script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
